<h2>Wedding and corporate events with Hi-Life Entertainment</h2>



<h3><em>New Craven Hall is an industrial, luxe events space exclusively for wedding and corporate in the heart of Leeds founded by Ben and Jane Corkhill in 2016</em></h3>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img data-attachment-id="237" data-permalink="https://hi-lifemobiledjleeds.blog/2020/03/11/new-craven-hall-2020/jane-ben-amber-marie-8/" data-orig-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/jane-ben-amber-marie-8.jpg" data-orig-size="3600,2400" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Amber Marie Photography - Amber&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 5D Mark III&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1526156788&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;All rights reserved&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;5000&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.005&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Jane &amp;amp; Ben &#8211; Amber Marie 8" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/jane-ben-amber-marie-8.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/jane-ben-amber-marie-8.jpg?w=1024" src="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/jane-ben-amber-marie-8.jpg" alt="Jane &amp; Ben - Amber Marie 8" class="wp-image-237 img-fluid" /></figure>



<p>Hi-Life Entertainment have been recommended suppliers at New Craven Hall since they launched this incredible venue in 2016. We provide all NCH clients with our completely tailored service for the type of music they wish to be played at their event. We issue all of our clients with a login to our unique online music planner. We can then take a look at the clients music and decide which of our DJs are most suited to host the event.&nbsp;This may sound like a simple procedure, but it needs to be closely&nbsp;looked at to ensure our clients are happy with the right DJ to host their special event.</p>



<p>We occasionally get more diverse&nbsp;lists from our clients which can sometimes be more specialist music. Some examples of this may include: Reggae, Ska, Indie Rock, Punk, Metal, R&amp;B, Grime, Drum &amp; Bass, Latin Jazz, Persian or Arabic music. We pride ourselves in making sure to provide music for any event no matter what the genre or theme. Most events at NCH throughout the year are mainly weddings, with corporate events, private and Christmas parties towards the end of the year.&nbsp;<a href="https://www.thehi-life.co.uk" rel="nofollow">https://www.thehi-life.co.uk</a></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img data-attachment-id="235" data-permalink="https://hi-lifemobiledjleeds.blog/2020/03/11/new-craven-hall-2020/img_8761/" data-orig-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/img_8761.jpeg" data-orig-size="4032,3024" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;1.8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;iPhone XR&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1572724278&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;4.25&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;320&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.04&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="IMG_8761" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/img_8761.jpeg?w=300" data-large-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/img_8761.jpeg?w=1024" src="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/img_8761.jpeg" alt="IMG_8761" class="wp-image-235 img-fluid" /></figure>



<p>New Craven Hall can cater for up to 200 seated or 250 standing guests, making this the perfect venue for many private events. You won’t find a more friendly hard working team who always aim to make your event a memorable day &amp; night to remember.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img data-attachment-id="238" data-permalink="https://hi-lifemobiledjleeds.blog/2020/03/11/new-craven-hall-2020/lauren-and-tom-from-the-smiths-26/" data-orig-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/lauren-and-tom-from-the-smiths-26.jpg" data-orig-size="801,1200" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;1.4&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;From The Smiths Photography&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;NIKON D750&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1555164272&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;From The Smiths Photography&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;35&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;2000&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0025&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Lauren and Tom- From the smiths (26)" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/lauren-and-tom-from-the-smiths-26.jpg?w=200" data-large-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/lauren-and-tom-from-the-smiths-26.jpg?w=684" src="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/lauren-and-tom-from-the-smiths-26.jpg" alt="Lauren and Tom- From the smiths (26)" class="wp-image-238 img-fluid" /></figure>



<p>This year New Craven Hall are proud to introduce our Silent Discos as an additional service to NCH packages with <em>&#8216;ZiggysSilentDiscos&#8217;</em> for a non-linear approach to more specialist music. This gives the client more flexibility with their music choices and up to 3 channels of music to choose from on our LED wireless headsets.<br>
No need to worry about having a <em>Katy Perry &#8211; California Gurls</em> and <em>Dead Kennedy’s &#8211; California Uber Alles</em> sound clash!</p>



<p>Simply switch the channel on your headset to tune into your desired taste of music.&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ziggyssilentdiscos.co.uk" rel="nofollow">https://www.ziggyssilentdiscos.co.uk</a></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img data-attachment-id="244" data-permalink="https://hi-lifemobiledjleeds.blog/2020/03/11/new-craven-hall-2020/led-headsets_01/" data-orig-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/led-headsets_01.jpeg" data-orig-size="4032,3024" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;1.8&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;iPhone XR&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1582835662&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;4.25&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;800&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.04&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="led headsets_01" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/led-headsets_01.jpeg?w=300" data-large-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/led-headsets_01.jpeg?w=1024" src="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/led-headsets_01.jpeg" alt="led headsets_01" class="wp-image-244 img-fluid" /></figure>



<p>We would recommend New Craven Hall to modern&nbsp;couples who wish to escape the traditional themed wedding reception that has plagued the UK for many years.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img data-attachment-id="247" data-permalink="https://hi-lifemobiledjleeds.blog/2020/03/11/new-craven-hall-2020/ben-jane/" data-orig-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/ben-jane.jpg" data-orig-size="1440,1435" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Ben &amp;amp; Jane" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/ben-jane.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/ben-jane.jpg?w=1024" src="https://hilife760731684.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/ben-jane.jpg" alt="Ben &amp; Jane" class="wp-image-247 img-fluid" /></figure>



<p>Ben and Jane will carefully&nbsp;assist you in decorating their canvas to suit your wedding theme. Look no further&nbsp;for a team who will ensure a memorable&nbsp;wedding that your guests will be talking about for many years to come. <a href="https://www.newcravenhall.co.uk" rel="nofollow">https://www.newcravenhall.co.uk</a></p>
